ary that transports viewers to a revolutionary energy project undertaken by GE and Huaneng Renewables.\n\nJust outside of Dali, China, these global energy leaders joined forces to construct an array of \u201csmart\u201d wind turbines. Connected through the industrial internet, these gentle giants leverage real-time data to calculate wind speed and grid demands, dynamically adapting to environmental conditions and consumer needs. The result: hyper-efficient green energy and the next generation of wind power production.", "short_description": "GE: Dali Windfarm Experience is a VR documentary that transports viewers to a revolutionary energy project undertaken by GE and Huaneng Renewables."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.ge.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.ge.com/terms", "publisher_name": "GE", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://ge.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "336338791550390"}, "review_messages": ["", "We experienced two significant issues while reviewing this application. First, after downloading the video it reached 100% and then the application became unresponsive. None of the on screen buttons worked and the back button on the headset did not allow the user to eturn to Oculus Home or the Universal Menu. After ~30-60 seconds, the application crashed. When re-launched the video was playable, but towards the end of the video (around the scene where the camera flies over the water after looking at the pagodas), the video stopped playing and brought the user to the main menu with a garbled/obscured error message.", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12533755_143025222872064_2757650865555767296_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YZNYBDsZBcgQ7kNvgFP3LrU&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDlpL3ZE5mHIdWJ43wSPV2x_FItw8db9Bi_wEOPqZ19Rg&oe=677E7E01"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "GE: Dali Windfarm Experience", "platform": "ANDROID", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_date": 1488960000, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "1391642650894521", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "1471354659542963", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "633317673536391"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "3121554321188303", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12533755_143025222872064_2757650865555767296_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YZNYBDsZBcgQ7kNvgFP3LrU&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDJxYI-rAeRkq_9NiteJq74eMGVs3GmUAdJnsLrb1Ze1Q&oe=677E7E01"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "1586816518143699", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12680493_215194728944847_7553460340961312768_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wl_FYvbdk-4Q7kNvgH0bTqZ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCaZoLwlXqwFJBdq02n5pD8CAp0WeDgXdAbDzLEkQbHLw&oe=677E5F1E"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "618184508739908", "image_type": "APP_IM